byline.contributor: Ben Strauss contributed reporting from Chicago, and Pete Wells and Elisa Cho from New York.

lead_paragraph: Questions linger in Chicago after the suicide of the inventive and ambitious star chef.

headline.print_headline: The Puzzling Death of Chicago’s Whirlwind Chef
headline.main: Puzzling Death of Chicago’s Whirlwind Chef, Homaro Cantu

snippet: Questions linger in Chicago after the suicide of the inventive and ambitious star chef.
abstract: Friends and family of Chicago chef Homaro Cantu still have questions about why he chose to commit suicide; many speculate about whether he had taken on too many responsibilities; large number of concurrent projects Cantu was juggling is not uncommon in age of celebrity chef, but overlooked in shadows of spotlight is immense stress that surrounds high-profile culinary endeavors.
